  def test_15_delete_cart_email_product_id(self):

    resp = trdemo_users_trdemo.get('/user/all')
    _email = jsonpath('$.[*].email', resp)

    # endpoint 14
    trdemo_shoppingcart_trdemo = get_http_target('TARGET_TRDEMO_SHOPPINGCART_TRDEMO', authenticate)

    # endpoint 15
